divs: Sighting DetailsI was watching the sky in my yard and I started to notice many faint star like lights that did not appear to blink travel very quickly across the sky. They all moved in different directions and at one point 3 of them got so close to each other that they nearly crossed paths. This is the second time I have seen these objects in the sky, however There were many more this time. What I found amazing was that right before I would see one, I would have a strong feeling that it was coming, almost sensing its presence.
